Fabric - GunGame Version
========================

V. 3.0 Final
------------




### > Gameplay:
The game takes place in an abandoned storage of washers and dryers in Africa, which is threatened by the earthquake.

Map by: nkpkiller / 2012 , POLAND

NOTE: There is 32 random spawn points.

### > Installation:
Decompress files:
gg_fabric_4d_v3.bsp
gg_fabric_4d_v3.nav
gg_fabric_4d_v3.txt

To your cstrike/maps folder.

Have fun!

nkpkiller, 2012 POLAND
